    title: 'Estimate at completion (typical-variance)',
    prompt: 'A project has a budget at completion (BAC) of $200,000 and a cumulative CPI of 0.8, and the cost variance is expected to continue. What is the estimate at completion (EAC)?',
    correct: '$250,000',
